news.headline: LA County Jury Hits Johnson & Johnson with Nearly $1 Billion Verdict
news.summary: LOS ANGELES, October 07, 2025--A Los Angeles County jury has returned damages totaling $966 million, including $950 million in punitive damages, to the family of Mae Moore, who died of mesothelioma in 2021 after using Johnson & Johnson’s iconic baby powder.
